{"sectionId":734,"sectionIdLiteral":"734","humanId":"lesson-313","volumeId":"workbook","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"title":"Now let a new perception come to me.","ownlineNumber":"Lesson 313"},"annotation":"W-313","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text lesson-313\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"734#1\"><p class=\"p-italic\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"734#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>Father, there is a vision which beholds all things as sinless, so that fear has gone, and where it was is love invited in.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"734#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>And love will come wherever it is asked.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"734#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>This vision is Your gift.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"734#1:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>The eyes of Christ look on a world forgiven.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"734#1:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>In His sight are all its sins forgiven, for He sees no sin in anything He looks upon.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"734#1:6\"><span class=\"snr\">6</span>Now let His true perception come to me, that I may waken from the dream of sin and look within upon my sinlessness, which You have kept completely undefiled upon the altar to Your holy Son, the Self with which I would identify.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"734#2\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">2.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"734#2:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>Let us today behold each other in the sight of Christ.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"734#2:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>How beautiful we are!</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"734#2:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>How holy and how loving!</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"734#2:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>Brother, come and join with me today.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"734#2:5\"><span class=\"snr\">5</span>We save the world when we have joined.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"734#2:6\"><span class=\"snr\">6</span>For in our vision it becomes as holy as the light in us.</span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"Father, there is a vision which beholds all things as sinless, so that fear has gone, and where it was is love invited in. And love will come wherever it is asked. This vision is Your gift. The eyes","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Lesson 313: Now let a new perception come to me | ACIM","seoDescription":"‚ú® A Course in Miracles with üéß Audio! Read and listen to Lesson¬†313 ‚ÄúNow let a new perception come to me‚Äù: Father, there is a vision which beholds all things as sinless, so that fear has‚Ä¶","desktopBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"10. What Is the Last Judgment?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":731,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-the-last-judgment"]}},{"label":"Lesson 313","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":734,"slugs":["lesson-313","now-let-a-new-perception-come-to-me"]}}],"mobileBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"10. What Is the Last Judgment?","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":731,"slugs":["workbook","what-is-the-last-judgment"]}},{"label":"Lesson 313","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":734,"slugs":["lesson-313","now-let-a-new-perception-come-to-me"]}}],"seoBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"A Course in Miracles","leadsTo":"dashboard"},{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part II","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":631,"slugs":["workbook","part-ii-introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"10. What Is 